rows.label: tlk45320151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hadashal Palace isn't just the imperial
residence, it's also Alba Margen's
best-defended stronghold.

rows.label: tlk45320151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If you visit the uppermost floor, you'll
be able to see the gigantic cannonports.

rows.label: tlk45320151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The elevators to the left and right will
take you up there, if you're interested.
